FT  11 JAN 94 / People: Huntleigh Technology
Julian Schildp finance director, is also appointed deputy chairman of
HUNTLEIGH TECHNOLOGY and John Wotton its group, md and chief executive of
HNE Healthcare. Gerard Wainwright, previously chief executive of the Nesbit
Evans Group, becomes joint md of HNE Healthcare UK on the acquisition of
Nesbit, and joins the group board.
